like Coastwood is your scene.

280
00:09:58.694 --> 00:10:00.360
- Oh. it's not.

281
00:10:00.394 --> 00:10:01.760
But my mom said I needed a strong senior year

282
00:10:01.793 --> 00:10:04.159
in order to get into a good college.

283
00:10:04.192 --> 00:10:05.493
So she landed an office job here.

284
00:10:05.526 --> 00:10:07.126
and that way. I get a major break on tuition.

285
00:10:07.159 --> 00:10:08.660
- Dad not in the picture?

286
00:10:08.692 --> 00:10:12.159
- No. he kind of lurks in the background like the Babadook.

287
00:10:12.192 --> 00:10:14.559
specializing in bad decisions and hot cougars.

288
00:10:14.592 --> 00:10:16.425
- Right.

289
00:10:16.458 --> 00:10:18.425
So you said Dakota found the body originally.

290
00:10:18.458 --> 00:10:21.424
- No. Dakota said CJ told her about it. who heard about it

291
00:10:21.457 --> 00:10:23.291
from Ilya and Autumn. who might have heard

292
00:10:23.324 --> 00:10:25.758
about it from somebody else.

293
00:10:25.791 --> 00:10:28.557
- So how many teenagers came out to the woods.

294
00:10:28.590 --> 00:10:30.823
