295
00:10:30.857 --> 00:10:31.757
except tell their friends?

296
00:10:31.790 --> 00:10:33.290
- Unknown.

297
00:10:33.323 --> 00:10:34.557
But I bet they all took selfies with it.

298
00:10:34.590 --> 00:10:36.557
- Starving.

299
00:10:36.590 --> 00:10:38.390
Can I order Green Juice or something?

300
00:10:38.423 --> 00:10:40.289
- Your intermittent fast doesn't end until 1:00.

301
00:10:40.322 --> 00:10:41.756
We can talk after that.

302
00:10:41.789 --> 00:10:44.622
- No one is asking you to spy on your friends.

303
00:10:44.656 --> 00:10:47.155
No. we have hidden surveillance set up to capture

304
00:10:47.188 --> 00:10:49.288
candid conversations. - Tight.

305
00:10:49.321 --> 00:10:51.121
But they're not my friends. - Oh.

306
00:10:51.154 --> 00:10:52.555
- How's my hair?

307
00:10:52.588 --> 00:10:54.154
- It's fine.

308
00:10:54.187 --> 00:10:55.421
Who are you trying to impress?

309
00:10:55.454 --> 00:10:56.654
- No one.

310
00:10:56.687 --> 00:10:57.554
Autumn.

311
00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.287
- She's pretty.

312
00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:04.554
- That's like saying that the Hanging Gardens of Babylon

313
00:11:04.587 --> 00:11:07.519
were cool instead of a feat of unparalleled engineering

314
00:11:07.553 --> 00:11:10.619
that redefined elegance and beauty in the ancient world.

315
00:11:10.653 --> 00:11:11.819
But I'm a little biased.

316
00:11:11.852 --> 00:11:14.486
- Clearly. She nice?

317
00:11:14.519 --> 00:11:17.285
- Hey. Dash. do you wanna come to my premiere tonight?

318
00:11:17.318 --> 00:11:19.218
- Uh. yeah. totally. I would love to.

319
00:11:19.251 --> 00:11:20.652
- No. wait.

320
00:11:20.685 --> 00:11:21.817
My publicist said we already did

321
00:11:21.851 --> 00:11:23.285
our charity work for the year.

322
00:11:23.318 --> 00:11:25.151
So you're out of luck. Sorry.

323
00:11:27.517 --> 00:11:28.551
- What are you premiering?

324
00:11:28.584 --> 00:11:30.150
- The new Laporte film.

325
00:11:30.183 --> 00:11:31.284
It's already getting Oscar buzz.

326
00:11:31.317 --> 00:11:32.484
- Oh. who do you play in the movie?

327
00:11:32.517 --> 00:11:33.683
- Young Addict Number Two.

328
00:11:33.716 --> 00:11:36.283
No lines. but my featured reactions

329
00:11:36.316 --> 00:11:37.650
really carry the film.

330
00:11:37.683 --> 00:11:40.283
Oh. by the way. I have a hard out at 3:00.

331
00:11:40.316 --> 00:11:42.149
Glam squad's coming to my house.

332
00:11:42.182 --> 00:11:43.349
- Well. we'll try to get you out in time

333
00:11:43.383 --> 00:11:45.382
