on top of his salary.

552
00:20:07.395 --> 00:20:09.628
- Why is "tutoring" in quotes?

553
00:20:09.661 --> 00:20:12.361
And one of the parents added a winky face emoji?

554
00:20:15.795 --> 00:20:17.760
- Every student who paid for tutoring got an A.

555
00:20:17.794 --> 00:20:20.328
- The only kid who was struggling was Dash.

556
00:20:20.361 --> 00:20:22.494
- Yeah. his mom was barely scraping tuition together.

557
00:20:22.527 --> 00:20:24.360
They couldn't afford anything extra.

558
00:20:24.393 --> 00:20:26.494
- Okay. so the parents are paying for grades

559
00:20:26.527 --> 00:20:28.360
so the kids get into a better college.

560
00:20:28.393 --> 00:20:30.493
But. I mean. why kill him?

561
00:20:30.526 --> 00:20:32.359
- Maybe he couldn't deliver.

562
00:20:32.392 --> 00:20:34.058
If I spent that kind of money and my kid

563
