didn't get into their dream school. I'd be pissed.

564
00:20:38.592 --> 00:20:41.492
- Reese. have you decided what college you're going to?

565
00:20:41.525 --> 00:20:44.492
- Um. I think I may be taking a gap year.

566
00:20:44.525 --> 00:20:46.090
- From your social media accounts.

567
00:20:46.123 --> 00:20:48.457
it seems like you're all about Yale.

568
00:20:48.491 --> 00:20:50.156
- That was kind of my mom's thing.

569
00:20:50.189 --> 00:20:51.757
- But you did apply.

570
00:20:51.791 --> 00:20:54.056
- Yeah. I applied to lots of places.

571
00:20:54.089 --> 00:20:57.456
but I didn't get in. so.

572
00:20:57.490 --> 00:20:59.690
- Was your mom upset?

573
00:20:59.723 --> 00:21:02.088
- Yeah. I guess.

574
00:21:02.121 --> 00:21:04.622
- Reese. we know it was you who started the rumor.

575
00:21:04.655 --> 00:21:06.289
- No. I heard it from CJ.

576
00:21:06.323 --> 00:21:08.755
- We know that's not true.

577
00:21:08.789 --> 00:21:13.222
But you did tell Dakota and Travis and Linette.

578
00:21:13.255 --> 00:21:16.222
You know what that tells me?

579
00:21:16.255 --> 00:21:18.721
You wanted someone to know.

580
00:21:18.754 --> 00:21:20.621
You wanted the police to know. but you just

581
