if you just say yes to the plea.

660
00:24:20.035 --> 00:24:21.301
- I mean. who cares there's no precedent for a felony

661
00:24:21.334 --> 00:24:23.401
prosecution this severe.

662
00:24:23.434 --> 00:24:24.734
